  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Housekeeping Attendant (Linen Room)",
  "description": "<p><br></p>\n<p>· To check linen received from the outside laundry. To spot check linen for damage or stains when item is received.</p>\n<p>· To ensure linens are properly stacked in the linen room, shelving and other related areas are clean.</p>\n<p>· To ensure proper control in the issuance of linen.</p>\n<p>· To report to the Housekeeping Shift Leader on heavily damaged or stained linens and to ensure that such items are recorded in the logbook.</p>\n<p>· To assist in the inventory of hotel linens.</p>\n<p>· To assist in the uniform attendant duties as needed.</p>\n<p>· To comply with hotel grooming standards.</p>\n<p>· To comply with hotel Fire Safety and Security procedures.</p>\n<p>· To perform all duties other than these above which are requested by the hotel management/direct supervisor.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Requirements: </p>\n<p>· Physical mobility and stamina required</p>\n<p>· Detail-oriented</p>\n<p>· Professional attitude is required</p>\n<p>· Ability to work independently</p>\n<p>· Excellent time management skills</p>\n<p>· Previous customer service experience may be required</p>\n<p><br></p>",
